    "title": "关于修订《京东开放平台个人/个体经营类目商品阈值明细表》的公示通知",
    "followRuleId": "1255762570669854720",
    "content": "<p style=\"line-height: 21pt; background: white; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">尊敬的商家：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 21pt; background: white; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">您好，为适应业务发展和满足商家经营需求，京东新增部分类目商品阈值，现修订</span><span style=\"color: black;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1211622812805107712\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">《京东开放平台个人/</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">个体经营类目商品阈值明细表》</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">，现进行规则公示，公示期：2025年7月7日- 2025年7月13日，规则预计于2025年7月14日生效，公示期满后平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 21pt; background: white; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">具体新增和调整情况见下表。</span></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 17.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 102.65pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.5pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"137\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">调整前后</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 102.65pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.5pt;\" width=\"137\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">一级类目</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 102.65pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.5pt;\" width=\"137\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">二级类目</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 102.65pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.5pt;\" width=\"137\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">类目阈值</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 102.65pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.5pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"137\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">新增</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 102.65pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.5pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"137\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">生鲜</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 102.65pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.5pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"137\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">蛋类</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 102.65pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.5pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"137\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">50</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 102.65pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.5pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"137\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">新增</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 102.65pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.5pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"137\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">生活日用</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 102.65pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.5pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"137\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">日用个护工具</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 102.65pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.5pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"137\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">300</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
